giving up a big chunk of last week's gains.
   The Dow Jones average of 30 industrials, up 29.34 points last
week, fell 23.47 to 2,074.68 by noontime on Wall Street.
   Losers outnumbered gainers by about 5 to 2 in the overall tally
of New York Stock Exchange-listed issues, with 342 up, 873 down and
