International Business Machines, down 1] at 112~.
   Reebok International dropped ~ to 11[. On Friday the company
projected lower earnings for the third quarter and the year.
   CSX jumped 3} to 30|. The company announced a restructuring
program that includes the planned repurchase of as many as 60
million shares, or about 38 percent of the total outstanding.
   The NYSE's composite index of all its listed common stocks fell
1.40 to 151.39. At the American Stock Exchange, the market value
index was down 1.31 at 296.91.
