percent, in value.
   The NYSE's composite index of all its listed common stocks
dropped .87 to 151.92.
   Standard & Poor's industrial index fell 2.36 to 308.45, and
S&P's 500-stock composite index was down 1.83 at 268.82.
   The NASDAQ composite index for the over-the-counter market
